{
  "stem": "12255.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- and the political aspect was being dealt with mainly from London and-- from Israel and from London.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were at-- I was at Diepholz for about a month, a month, six weeks, or so.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the civilians came in, then I--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--returned to military duties.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was posted to a place called Iserlohn, in the rural area.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I, I travelled around the whole area, an area about half the size of [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Natale, ?] wherever Jewish boys were stationed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- at various centers, I used to organize Shabbat Eve services, Shabbat morning services, and Shabbat afternoon services and keep the boys in touch with Judaism.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the first Rosh Hashanah New Year services I held in a barracks at a place called Munster, M-U-N-S-T-E-R, quite a large town.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had the-- about 400 soldiers, Jewish soldiers, attended that service because they were still-- the army hadn't started really heavily demobilizing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember that--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1945, Rosh Hashanah, 1945.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, 1945.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember the-- the-- this big hall where we held it was part of the barracks, but it was also the only sort of communal hall left.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had put up big blue and white flags, you know, over the platform.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that very evening, there-- after the end of Rosh Hashanah, there was a big musical concert, a German, you know-- organized.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we left the flags all in place for them to see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was involved with the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But unofficially we knew what was going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But officially we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because those people, many, many people, A, from Bergen-Belsen and other camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
